video.title: Ancient Aliens: Collection
video.synopsis: This compelling series explores the possibility that aliens came to Earth in ancient times and influenced our scientific and cultural development.

episodes.synopsis: If ancient aliens visited Earth, did they leave behind clues that exist in plain sight, such as sophisticated aircraft and complex electrical grids?
episodes.title: The Evidence

episodes.synopsis: Reports of encounters with strange beings and sightings of mysterious objects in the sky have occurred throughout history.
episodes.title: Closer Encounters

episodes.synopsis: There is evidence that suggests we experienced recent alien contact. In 1942, the Battle of L.A. involved the US military allegedly fighting a UFO.
episodes.title: The Return

episodes.synopsis: Explore subterranean realms that may hold proof of alien visitation, such as an Ecuadoran cave where investigators discovered strange metallic books.
episodes.title: Underground Aliens

episodes.synopsis: If ancient aliens visited Earth, can evidence of their existence be found in the mysterious structures that still stand throughout the world?
episodes.title: Unexplained Structures

episodes.synopsis: Visits from aliens and their spacecraft might be behind ancient legends and myths of Garuda-like flying creatures and monsters like Medusa.
episodes.title: Aliens and Monsters

episodes.synopsis: Laser-like cuts at an ancient Peruvian fortress, an acoustic room in Malta and heat-shielding traits of Mexican pyramids may reveal alien engineering.
episodes.title: Aliens and Ancient Engineers

episodes.synopsis: Local myths of malevolent places like Australia's Black Mountains and a forest that attracts would-be suicides may record past alien contact.
episodes.title: Aliens and Evil Places

episodes.synopsis: Stories of zombies, vampires and other undead beings might only embody human fears, or they could signify contact with soulless extraterrestrials.
episodes.title: Aliens and the Undead

episodes.synopsis: Could the ancient Mayans, with their complex calendars and advanced knowledge of science and mathematics, have traveled to the Milky Way?
episodes.title: The Mayan Conspiracy

episodes.synopsis: The ruins of Puma Punku in Peru baffle researchers who, combining computer analyses and local myths, suggest an extraterrestrial origin for the site.
episodes.title: The Mystery of Puma Punku

episodes.synopsis: Artifacts from ancient cultures depict creatures resembling dinosaurs, leading to a theory that aliens killed them to allow humans to prosper.
episodes.title: Aliens and Dinosaurs

episodes.synopsis: Because many ancient civilizations closely observed the Orion constellation, theorists speculate that it might have been a "stargate" for aliens.
episodes.title: Destination Orion

episodes.synopsis: The Nazca lines in the Peruvian desert depict gigantic figures, animals and geometric patterns that some theorize may have a link to aliens.
episodes.title: Beyond Nazca

episodes.synopsis: Theorists wonder if massive stone monuments created by ancient civilizations around the world have a connection to extraterrestrials.
episodes.title: The Monoliths
